Quote: Although members appear distrustful of each other, and have as yet made no formal attempt to meet on common ground in party organisation, there is no doubt that a great deal of quiet "sounding" is going on, and that there are .. a few shrewd heads engaged in gathering up the threads of individual opinion, in the hope of being able to weave out of them some tie which would bind a majority.
